ultiple serotonergic agents should be avoided if possible, or otherwise approached with caution if potential benefit is deemed to outweigh the risk.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/143001/', '', 'Vilazodone, Esketamine', 'Viloxazine, Nefazodone', 1767369485);
